Step you need to take:


* Start a new dir
npm init -y
npm install -D hardhat

* Paste the hardhat.config.js
npx hardhat --> see if this command works
* Paste the 'contracts' and 'test' dir

npm install -D @nomiclabs/hardhat-ethers ethers @nomiclabs/hardhat-waffle ethereum-waffle chai
npm install hardhat-gas-reporter --save-dev
npm install @ethersproject/address web3

Run:
npx hardhat compile --> to compile
npx hardhat test --> to compile AND deploy AND test